on class=\"hero\">\n  <div class=\"content\">\n    <div class=\"rating-badge\"><span class=\"stars\">★★★★★</span><strong>4.2</strong> <span style=\"opacity:.8\">&middot; 915 avis Google</span></div>\n    <div class=\"eyebrow\">Restaurant &middot; Casablanca</div>\n    <h1>Relais de Paris</h1>\n    <p class=\"sub\">Une adresse que les Casablancais adorent — authenticité, saveurs, et accueil chaleureux.</p>\n    <div class=\"btns\">\n      <a href=\"https://wa.me/212522368796\" class=\"btn btn-primary\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">💬 Réserver sur WhatsApp</a>\n      <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"btn btn-ghost\">Nous trouver</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"about\" class=\"about\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"about-grid\">\n      <div class=\"img\" style=\"background-image:url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFkwknd30rg3d3epZcrtVk-VLfvxbbJ5Vzxr-h8Vxm_rBXc_2knqg_nyIG2tjGCqiP04rDmCqKxuWeWyK0AOVaak1Xxy_5e6fgQves-pf1NhKWoRI7L7fY64NjMw7PQXxEuGZE-=w1920-h1080-k-no')\"></div>\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"color:#8b2635;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.25em;font-size:.8rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px\">Notre histoire</div>\n        <h2 style=\"font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.8rem);margin-bottom:22px\">Bien plus qu'un restaurant</h2>\n        <p>Relais de Paris s'est imposé comme une référence à Casablanca. Avec <strong>4.2★ sur 915 avis Google</strong>, notre établissement doit son succès à la qualité constante, à la fraîcheur de ses produits, et à une équipe qui met l'humain au cœur de chaque visite.</p>\n        <p>Que ce soit pour un déjeuner rapide, un dîner en famille, ou un moment partagé entre amis, nous vous promettons une expérience authentique — celle qui donne envie de revenir.</p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top:18px\"><strong>📍 Av. Habib Sinaceur, Casablanca, Morocco</strong></p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"gallery\" class=\"gallery\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"color:#f5d7a0\">Galerie</div>\n      <h2>L'œil dans l'assiette</h2>\n      <p style=\"color:#aaa\">Quelques instants capturés chez nous.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"gal-grid\"><div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFkwknd30rg3d3epZcrtVk-VLfvxbbJ5Vzxr-h8Vxm_rBXc_2knqg_nyIG2tjGCqiP04rDmCqKxuWeWyK0AOVaak1Xxy_5e6fgQves-pf1NhKWoRI7L7fY64NjMw7PQXxEuGZE-=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Relais de Paris\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipMP10RPDfHWRG_fHe3qZcKZ0edQSl_wtCkvFi__=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Relais de Paris\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAFAvecuVp6wrODBWg387d58vngHi-IPFgz3XCmHO54nK1ZxqT3Bz3zV6cy6pBg71yVJy-hIYLYde1aI19EtuJSFyA4L5sFzTnOnbPHcALLoO8tDw5Dl_dhSuBNN7_9qnfQSU7gPWpWHKqxK=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Relais de Paris\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAH5a-8QaDLHUUw1RA5WFv_St5W67w47yga5lrpePyL6Fapgt7qiLGCR38RWoGQF7174wcHpmk5n3LZ_u5Gxb98vSjNn31I3gdodeS14JoR8mP3piiVp72iip3aRc-UDnkQWbdQg8WLQlyj3=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Relais de Paris\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNvlzDi22mSl9sPk8GwxC7jybVyurbDnkunhwBR=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Relais de Paris\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGKN_4082e8wq3XhMUDKYLrCPtV6x-DmmIXG-pnvGha1JqoWV48jfa8zbGJC6UPjwbxaS-_yN-B0Chc-vRvKNLBS7HFwHMfMu7WVenXg42zo-wosYWnWqSF0poThTwSISVTomxv=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Relais de Paris\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGgwHu1uzjvxwcgMsj2vvwpdB8spGO_zdDmly2cpW4lW8bq4_DfOHg_QrKa7RTMXsEtU_yCOGLlLupkGwy9JIyH4PFnXUHJQk9FfC-I2G1lFnNC78kiMFcMEs3XIljbDkxr5snp=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Relais de Paris\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNwuC8nijO4-1Fyz5eiwbu4GiXlM3dBrG1sYwrJ=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Relais de Paris\"></div>\n<div class=\"gal-item\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipO8GsczHk8PK38pI3mIfEbt_bdITeCsy1U5x8-r=w1920-h1080-k-no\" alt=\"Relais de Paris\"></div></div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"reviews\" class=\"reviews\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div class=\"eyebrow\">Ils en parlent</div>\n      <h2>Ce que disent nos clients</h2>\n      <p>Avis vérifiés Google — 915 retours et comptant.</p>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"rev-grid\"><div class=\"review\"><div class=\"stars\">★★★★☆</div><p>\"The setting is pleasant and the atmosphere refined. The staff is professional and attentive, although their close presence can sometimes be a little intrusive.\n\nThe dishes offered are typical of French cuisine, well-executed and expertly prepared.\n\nSpecial mention goes to the profiteroles for dessert, which were absolutely excellent—a true triumph.\"</p><div class=\"author\">— Dp</div></div>\n<div class=\"review\"><div class=\"stars\">★☆☆☆☆</div><p>\"Never coming back, I&#x27;ve never seen such a obnoxious place where the staff are being treated with bad manners by the manager. Finger snapping, rude behaviour towords the staff from the upper manager. Bouncing around like a little man on steroids. He should be ashamed of himself. My party sat down and we had to go to the kitchen to order, nobody noticed us because they were too busy ordering the cle\"</p><div class=\"author\">— Ruup</div></div>\n<div class=\"review\"><div class=\"stars\">★★☆☆☆</div><p>\"The meat lacked flavor, unfortunately I didn&#x27;t finish my meal\"</p><div class=\"author\">— sara. sakri</div></div>\n<div class=\"review\"><div class=\"stars\">★☆☆☆☆</div><p>\"I&#x27;ve been coming to Relais de Paris for years, and I&#x27;ve noticed a steady decline in quality. Today is definitely the last time I&#x27;ll ever set foot in there. The food was inedible and the prices exorbitant. A meat dish cost 300 dirhams. We asked for it medium-rare, but it was served rare. The half roast chicken dish had absolutely no flavor. They seriously need to rethink their approach to cooking. \"</p><div class=\"author\">— Adil KHAOULANI</div></div></div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n  <div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"section-head\">\n      <div class=\"eyebrow\" style=\"color:#f5d7a0\">Nous rejoindre</div>\n      <h2>Venez nous voir</h2>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"contact-grid\">\n      <div class=\"contact-info\">\n        <h3>Informations</h3>\n        <div class=\"item\"><span class=\"icon\">📍</span><div><strong>Adresse</strong><br>Av. Habib Sinaceur, Casablanca, Morocco</div></div>\n        <div class=\"item\"><span class=\"icon\">📞</span><div><strong>Téléphone</strong><br><a href=\"tel:+212522368796\">+212 5 22 36 87 96</a></div></div>\n        <div class=\"item\"><span class=\"icon\">🕐</span><div><strong>Horaires</strong><ul class='hours'><li><strong>Monday</strong><span>12 to 11 PM</span></li><li><strong>Tuesday</strong><span>12 to 11 PM</span></li><li><strong>Wednesday</strong><span>12 to 11 PM</span></li><li><strong>Thursday</strong><span>12 to 11 PM</span></li><li><strong>Friday</strong><span>12 to 11 PM</span></li><li><strong>Saturday</strong><span>12 to 11 PM</span></li><li><strong>Sunday</strong><span>12 to 11 PM</span></li></ul></div></div>\n        <a href=\"https://wa.me/212522368796\" class=\"wa-cta\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">💬 Écrivez-nous sur WhatsApp</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"map-wrap\">\n        <iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps?q=Relais+de+Paris%2C+Av.+Habib+Sinaceur%2C+Casablanca%2C+Morocco&amp;output=embed\" loading=\"lazy\" 